# Sweet Cravings Bakery Changelog
All notable changes to the **Sweet Cravings Bakery** website project will be documented in this file.

## [1.0.0] â€” Initial Development and Progressive Enhancements

### Overview
The project establishes a fully functional, multi-page bakery website featuring a modern design, intuitive navigation, and visually engaging elements. The primary goal of this release is to build the complete foundation of the website, including structure, styling, responsiveness, and interactive components.

---

## âœ¨ Major Updates & Features

### 1. Complete Website Structure
- Added full multi-page architecture:
  - **index.html** â€“ Homepage with welcome content and gallery.
  - **location.html** â€“ Bakery address, business hours, embedded Google Map.
  - **contact.html** â€“ Contact details, social links, and fully functioning contact form.
  - **about.html** & **products.html** â€“ Initial templates prepared for future expansion.
- Established consistent navigation across all pages.

---

### 2. Sample Content & Visual Assets
- Added placeholder images to the `images/` directory.
- Populated pages with descriptive bakery-themed content.
- Ensured all images have descriptive **alt** attributes for SEO and accessibility.

---

### 3. Image Gallery with Lightbox
- Implemented an interactive gallery on the homepage:
  - Thumbnails open a **modal lightbox** with full-size images.
  - Modal includes a close button and click-outside-to-exit behavior.
- Added smooth fade-in/out transitions for improved user experience.
- Improved gallery navigation and visual consistency.

---

### 4. Responsive & Aesthetic Styling
- Created a comprehensive **style.css** file with:
  - Clean, modern UI design.
  - Fully responsive layout for desktop, tablet, and mobile.
  - Centered elements (images, GIFs, headings) for symmetry.
  - Cohesive color palette supporting bakery branding.
  - Hover effects for navigation and gallery items.
- Added media queries for improved layout on small screens.

---

### 5. SEO & Social Media Optimization
- Added essential meta tags:
  - Description, keywords, author.
  - Open Graph tags for social sharing.
- Used semantic HTML elements for accessibility and SEO.
- Optimized image file sizes to improve load speed.

---

### 6. Interactive Contact Form
- Built a polished form with fields for name, email, subject, and message.
- Styled with clear visual hierarchy.
- Implemented JavaScript for:
  - Input validation.
  - Success confirmation message.
  - Automatic form reset after submission.

---

### 7. Visual & Functional Styling Enhancements
- Added animations and hover transitions to images and buttons.
- Styled lightbox overlay with subtle transparency.
- Centered GIFs using CSS Flexbox for consistency across pages.
- Integrated Google Fonts for improved typography.

---

### 8. Accessibility & Usability Improvements
- Ensured all interactive elements have visible focus states.
- Added descriptive alt text across all imagery.
- Improved keyboard navigation structure.
- Maintained strong contrast ratios for readability.

---

### 9. Code Quality & Maintenance
- Organized all HTML, CSS, and JS files with comments.
- Modularized scripts to support future scalability.
- Ensured cross-browser compatibility.

